"For graphical stuff
colorscheme kashif
"Set the font and size
set guifont="Monospace 11"

"Hide toolbar
set guioptions-=T
set numberwidth=4 "Highlight current line
set cursorline

"Turn on spell checking with English dictionary
"set spell
"set spelllang=en
"set spellsuggest=9 "show only 9 suggestions for misspelled words
